@startuml svc-scheduling-orchestrator--post-schedule-requests

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2563eb
}

header [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#integration-context ⬆ svc-scheduling-orchestrator Integration Context]]

title POST /schedule-requests\nRequest optimal daily schedule\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with parallel lookup and constraint logic</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-scheduling-orchestrator" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/]] #DBEAFE
participant "Trip Catalog" as TC [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Guide Mgmt" as GM [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/]] #E0E7FF
participant "Trail Mgmt" as TM [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Weather Svc" as WX [[/microservices/svc-weather/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PG + Valkey" as DB [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-scheduling-orchestrator.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /schedule-requests
activate GW #2563eb
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #2563eb

note right of Svc : Validate request\n(trip_id, date, required_guides)

== Trip Requirements ==

Svc -> TC : [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/#get-tripstrip_id-get-trip-details GET /trips/{trip_id}]]
activate TC #FEF3C7
TC --> Svc : Trip details\n(adventure_category, trail_id,\ndifficulty, min_guides, max_participants)
deactivate TC

== Parallel Upstream Lookups ==

note right of Svc : These three calls execute\nin parallel via CompletableFuture

Svc -> GM : [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/#get-guidesguide_idavailability-check-guide-availability GET /guides/{id}/availability]]
activate GM #E0E7FF
Svc -> TM : [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#get-trailstrail_idconditions-get-trail-conditions GET /trails/{id}/conditions]]
activate TM #FEF3C7
Svc -> WX : [[/microservices/svc-weather/#get-weatherforecast-get-weather-forecast GET /weather/forecast]]
activate WX #F1F5F9

GM --> Svc : Guide availability\n(available guides with\ncertifications and preferences)
deactivate GM
TM --> Svc : Trail conditions\n(status, safety_rating,\nlast_inspection)
deactivate TM
WX --> Svc : Weather forecast\n(conditions, wind, precipitation,\nlightning_risk)
deactivate WX

== Constraint Evaluation ==

alt Trail CLOSED or safety_rating < minimum
    note right of Svc #FEE2E2 : Schedule cannot be created\nTrail conditions unsafe
    Svc --> GW : 422 Unprocessable\n(reason: TRAIL_UNSAFE)
    deactivate Svc
    GW --> Client : 422 Unprocessable
    deactivate GW
else Weather forecast severe
    note right of Svc #FEF3C7 : Flag as WEATHER_ADVISORY\nSchedule created with\nweather warning attached
else All constraints pass
    note right of Svc #D1FAE5 : Proceed with\nguide assignment
end

note right of Svc : Guide selection criteria:\n1. Certification matches trip type\n2. Trail familiarity (prior trips)\n3. Language match with guests\n4. Workload balance

== Database ==

group Transaction boundary
    Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO schedule_requests\n(request_id, trip_id, date,\nassigned_guides, trail_status,\nweather_advisory, status = CONFIRMED)
    activate DB #FEF9C3
    DB --> Svc : Created row
    deactivate DB
end

== Async Notifications ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Notify assigned guides]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created\n(request_id, assigned_guides,\nweather_advisory, status)
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml
